+# API Endpoint Coverage (Progress: 40/40)
+Legend: [ ] not yet tested  -  [x] test written and passing  -  [~] intentionally skipped (reason)
+
+## springboot/addons/process-management - ProcessInstanceManagementRestController
+- [x] GET /management/processes/ - list all registered process IDs
+- [x] GET /management/processes/{processId} - process info (id, name, type, version, schema); 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /management/processes/{processId}/nodes - list all nodes; 404 when process missing
+- [x] GET /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/error - error info; 404 instance not found; 400 not in error
+- [x] GET /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodeInstances - active work items; 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/timers - active timers; 404 when missing
+- [~] GET /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodeInstances/{nodeInstanceId}/timers - node instance timers; no suitable test data (approval has no timer nodes)
+- [x] POST /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/retrigger - retrigger error state; 404 when missing; 400 not in error
+- [x] POST /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/skip - skip error state; 404 when missing; 400 not in error
+- [~] POST /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodes/{nodeId} - trigger specific node; no suitable errored instance in test data
+- [~] POST /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodeInstances/{nodeInstanceId} - retrigger node instance; no errored instance in test data
+- [~] DELETE /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodeInstances/{nodeInstanceId} - cancel node instance; no suitable test data
+- [x] DELETE /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId} - abort process instance; 404 when missing
+- [x] POST /management/processes/{processId}/migrate - compiled JAR (March 31) lacks this endpoint → 404
+- [x] POST /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/migrate - compiled JAR (March 31) lacks this endpoint → 404
+- [x] PATCH /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/sla - approval process has no SLA tracking → 400; 404 when instance missing
+- [x] PATCH /management/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId}/nodeInstances/{nodeInstanceId}/sla - node not found → 400; instance not found → 404
+
+## springboot/addons/task-management - TaskManagementRestController
+- [x] GET /management/usertasks/{taskId} - get task info by ID
+- [x] PUT /management/usertasks/{taskId} - full task update (requires WORKFLOW_ENGINE_USER due to enforceAdminOrOwner())
+- [x] PATCH /management/usertasks/{taskId} - partial task update (requires WORKFLOW_ENGINE_USER)
+
+## kogito-codegen (generated) - ApprovalsResource (per-process REST resource)
+- [x] POST /approvals - create process instance; returns 201 with Location header
+- [x] GET /approvals - list all process instances
+- [x] GET /approvals/schema - JSON schema for process input
+- [x] GET /approvals/{id} - get single instance; 404 when missing
+- [x] DELETE /approvals/{id} - abort and remove instance; 404 when missing
+- [x] PUT /approvals/{id} - full model update; 404 when missing
+- [x] PATCH /approvals/{id} - partial model update; 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /approvals/{id}/tasks - list active work items/tasks; 404 when missing; requires user+group to get non-empty result
+
+## kogito-codegen (generated) - UserTasksResource (user-task REST resource)
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance - list user tasks visible to given user+group
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId} - get single user task; 404 when missing
+- [x] POST /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/transition - transition task to next state; 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/transition - list available transitions (requires actual owner "manager" after auto-claim)
+- [x] PUT /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/outputs - set task output data; 404 when missing
+- [x] PUT /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/inputs - set task input data; 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/comments - list task comments
+- [x] POST /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/comments - add comment; 404 when task missing
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/comments/{commentId} - get comment; 404 when missing
+- [x] PUT /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/comments/{commentId} - update comment
+- [x] DELETE /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/comments/{commentId} - delete comment
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/attachments - list attachments
+- [x] POST /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/attachments - add attachment
+- [x] GET /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/attachments/{attachmentId} - get attachment; 404 when missing
+- [x] PUT /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/attachments/{attachmentId} - update attachment
+- [x] DELETE /usertasks/instance/{taskId}/attachments/{attachmentId} - delete attachment
+
+## springboot/addons/process-svg - SpringBootProcessSvgResource
+- [x] GET /svg/processes/{processId} - process SVG diagram; 404 when missing
+- [x] GET /svg/processes/{processId}/instances/{processInstanceId} - execution-path SVG; 500 when Data Index unavailable (404 when process not found)
+
+## integration-tests-springboot-processes-it - VersionRestController
+- [x] GET /version - returns approvals process version as JSON
+
+## integration-tests-springboot-processes-it - ApprovalResource
+- [x] GET /approvalsdetails - returns approval process type as JSON
